2. cs.SI (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the performance of a coding scheme for multiuser MIMO systems, which is a topic within systems and control. 
3. cs.NT (Number Theory) - The paper uses algebraic number theory to construct lattice codes, which is a topic within number theory. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the transmission of signals over a multiuser MIMO system, which is a topic within multimedia. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper discusses the construction of lattice codes, which have applications in cryptography and security.
